channel.title: Greatxscape 718 fun server
channel.description:
The maker of SupremeScape is back with another server! In colaboration with the owner of GreatXScape we are once again striving for a fun and enjoyable server. Don't think we haven't do anything in the meanwhile, we have been doing nothing else than developing this server. Come take a look and take a trip back into time. Let the nostalgia begin!
Features:
- Bossing - All other bosses we all know are availible - 25/25 Skills working - Dungeoneering where you can choose what you want to kill - The Abyss 100% like RS - Full Living Rock Caverns - Clue Scrolls - Over 20 NPC caves - Refurbished donator features - Weekly events - Daily Updates
Please go to www.greatxscape.org to download client and get started :D
